ns over blocks of data transmission. Therefore, we provide a novel\nsolution that allows with limited cooperation: a significant reduction in the\nCSI feedback from the receiver to the transmitter, and timely optimal designs\nof the precoding and power allocation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Nov 2014 18:20:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Nov 2014 11:12:37 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 11 Jan 2016 17:37:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-12"}
