hmarks for Uncertainty\nAnalysis in Modeling (UAM) for the Design, Operation and Safety Analysis of\nLWRs\" is studied as an example application. The burn-up simulations are\nperformed with the SCALE 6.0 tool suite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Nov 2014 09:33:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-08"}
