131 by examining\ntransmission dynamics between hosts to achieve a goal of pre-empting resistance\nbefore it emerges by optimising antimicrobial treatment protocols.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Nov 2014 13:39:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 16 Feb 2015 11:56:17 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 17 Feb 2015 09:32:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-18"}
